                    <h4 class="service-heading">公開透明</h4>
                    <p class="value_explanation text-muted">公開每筆交易的金額流向，您將不再多花冤枉錢</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-1">
                    <%=image_tag 'index/plus.png'%>
